author: Times-News
title: Elon stumbles vs. Towson in women's soccer
text: Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 12:27 AM Updated at 12:28 AM Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 12:27 AM Updated at 12:28 AM TOWSON, Md. — The Elon women’s soccer team came up short as the Phoenix lost 1-0 to host Towson in a Colonial Athletic Association game Sunday at the Tiger Soccer Complex. With the loss, Elon (9-7-2 overall, 1-6-1 CAA) was eliminated from the CAA Women’s Soccer Championships. VasthyDelgado found the net in the 67th minute to give the Tigers (7-8-4, 1-6-2) the victory. Towson outshot Elon 19-16 in the contest. By Times-News
